reviewText: I did the 5 star rating  because it's good & pretty well clean entertainment & not a lot of senseless violence & killing,also no stupid cuss words( so why do they call that adult language??? ). If You love mystery and spy story's done in 25 mins or so then this may be Your cup of tea. PS, each of the shows is in black & white but the picture is great.
boring don't bother with this even if it is low priced much better stuff from the 50s tv sereis are available online try it!
